{
  "texts": [
    "Here, Binoculars uses the default decision threshold and the PLM is not further fine-tuned.",
    "The best detection accuracy for each generator, in each scenario, is in bold.",
    "tectors perform marginally better than GPTZero, but still with a maximum accuracy of 61% (Bino.).",
    "This indicates that off-the-shelf methods, which do not require knowledge of the generating LLM, are not reliable detectors of social media texts generated by fine-tuned models (RQ3).",
    "The previous two sections establish opposite ends of the classification results spectrum: the completeknowledge scenario, and the no-knowledge scenario."
